1
00:00:06,600 --> 00:00:11,537
=The Moment I Met You=

2
00:00:11,537 --> 00:00:14,962
=Episode 34=

3
00:00:28,640 --> 00:00:29,359
Stop it!

4
00:00:31,199 --> 00:00:32,880
Wushuang, what are you doing?

5
00:00:36,160 --> 00:00:37,920
Director Liu,
I am interrogating a prisoner.

6
00:00:37,920 --> 00:00:38,840
Stay out of this.

7
00:00:39,479 --> 00:00:41,960
Miss Luo, Chu Yunchang has already
been sentenced to death.

8
00:00:41,960 --> 00:00:43,719
Why use extrajudicial torture on her?

9
00:00:45,320 --> 00:00:46,560
I'm just furious.

10
00:00:47,150 --> 00:00:48,510
If the Commissioner finds out,

11
00:00:48,662 --> 00:00:50,262
how will you answer for this?

12
00:00:50,880 --> 00:00:51,679
I'm not afraid.

13
00:00:52,640 --> 00:00:54,000
My grandfather won't blame me.

14
00:00:54,000 --> 00:00:54,600
Then,

15
00:00:56,280 --> 00:00:57,679
what if Mao Buyu finds out?

16
00:00:58,039 --> 00:01:00,200
If Chu Yunchang
is executed by Imperial decree,

17
00:01:00,640 --> 00:01:02,039
Mao Buyu won't say anything.

18
00:01:02,640 --> 00:01:03,840
But if she dies by your hand,

19
00:01:04,280 --> 00:01:05,000
do you think

20
00:01:05,437 --> 00:01:07,797
Mao Buyu will still like you?

21
00:01:14,359 --> 00:01:15,480
When is the execution?

22
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,719
Tomorrow.

23
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:18,760
Fine.

24
00:01:20,439 --> 00:01:23,120
I'll let this female thief
live one more day.

25
00:01:24,200 --> 00:01:25,239
Take it easy, you two.

26
00:01:25,937 --> 00:01:26,577
Move aside.

27
00:01:28,680 --> 00:01:29,319
Yunchang,

28
00:01:29,462 --> 00:01:30,742
how are you feeling?

29
00:01:55,799 --> 00:01:56,480
Thank you.

30
00:01:56,959 --> 00:01:58,200
There's no need for thanks.

31
00:01:59,000 --> 00:02:00,439
She has been sentenced to death

32
00:02:00,439 --> 00:02:01,920
and will be executed tomorrow.

33
00:02:02,319 --> 00:02:04,319
I simply don't want her to suffer

34
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,159
any more pain before she dies.

35
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:09,120
Do you have anything else to say?

36
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:16,560
Then, I shall take my leave.

37
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:22,599
Both Sacred Tokens
are at the Gate Bureau.

38
00:02:33,199 --> 00:02:34,080
What did you say?

39
00:02:34,780 --> 00:02:36,879
The Sacred Tokens
that can command the martial world

40
00:02:37,319 --> 00:02:38,840
are at the Gate Bureau.

41
00:02:39,879 --> 00:02:41,960
Well, isn't that
a happy ending for everyone?

42
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,639
Do you even know what I'm talking about?

43
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,919
It doesn't matter anymore.

44
00:02:46,680 --> 00:02:48,240
You're being executed tomorrow.

45
00:02:48,759 --> 00:02:49,919
Save those words

46
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,919
to tell the King of the Underworld.

47
00:03:04,599 --> 00:03:05,879
Have you thoroughly investigated

48
00:03:06,700 --> 00:03:08,190
everything I ordered you to look into?

49
00:03:08,650 --> 00:03:09,360
Yes, Your Majesty.

50
00:03:15,762 --> 00:03:17,287
(Petition from Embroidered Guard Mao Buyu
of the Northern Constabulary Office)

51
00:03:21,319 --> 00:03:22,680
You already have a plan?

52
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,639
That's right.

53
00:03:24,120 --> 00:03:24,879
It's just...

54
00:03:25,479 --> 00:03:26,319
Go ahead and do it.

55
00:03:26,600 --> 00:03:29,180
I have restored your rank
as Commander of the Embroidered Guard.

56
00:03:29,290 --> 00:03:30,639
There's no need for any concerns.

57
00:03:31,639 --> 00:03:32,599
Thank you, Your Majesty.

58
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,199
Master!

59
00:03:38,159 --> 00:03:39,199
You're finally back.

60
00:03:39,479 --> 00:03:40,240
What's wrong?

61
00:03:40,390 --> 00:03:41,840
Yunchang has been sentenced to death.

62
00:03:42,580 --> 00:03:43,639
The execution is tomorrow.

63
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,120
What did you say?

64
00:04:06,919 --> 00:04:08,120
Chang.

65
00:04:08,520 --> 00:04:09,439
Chang, wake up!

66
00:04:10,319 --> 00:04:10,919
Chang.

67
00:04:29,120 --> 00:04:29,839
Wushuang.

68
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,399
You really did come to break her out.

69
00:04:38,759 --> 00:04:39,990
What have you done to Yunchang?

70
00:04:41,199 --> 00:04:41,879
Don't worry.

71
00:04:42,879 --> 00:04:44,399
She won't be killed until tomorrow.

72
00:04:45,439 --> 00:04:46,160
Mao Buyu,

73
00:04:46,600 --> 00:04:48,480
as a constable,
you knowingly broke the law

74
00:04:48,790 --> 00:04:49,959
by openly raiding the prison.

75
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:51,839
Your crime is unpardonable.

76
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:53,240
Someone, come.

77
00:04:53,519 --> 00:04:55,040
Throw Mao Buyu into the male cell

78
00:04:55,360 --> 00:04:56,439
to await his sentencing.

79
00:05:05,199 --> 00:05:05,959
Chu Xiangling?

80
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,839
Chief Mao, Coroner Xu,

81
00:05:10,959 --> 00:05:12,279
it's been a long time.

82
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,800
I hope you've been well.

83
00:05:21,000 --> 00:05:21,920
Good tea.

84
00:05:28,279 --> 00:05:29,079
Mao Buyu...

85
00:05:32,240 --> 00:05:33,839
He has disappointed me so much.

86
00:05:36,199 --> 00:05:37,800
But you still like him.

87
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:42,399
What should I do, Grandfather?

88
00:05:43,399 --> 00:05:44,959
Tomorrow, Chu Yunchang will be executed,

89
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,220
and Mao Buyu will lose his post.

90
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,839
The Mao family name will be struck
from the Gate Bureau.

91
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:51,839
If he wants to restore
his family's prestige,

92
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,040
he must marry you

93
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,199
and join the Luo family.

94
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,079
That is his only way out.

95
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:01,000
And if he refuses?

96
00:06:01,759 --> 00:06:02,930
Then, whether he lives or dies

97
00:06:03,439 --> 00:06:04,920
will be entirely up to you.

98
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:14,439
You heard everything?

99
00:06:16,000 --> 00:06:16,720
Grandfather.

100
00:06:17,279 --> 00:06:19,439
My master and Chu Yunchang are in love.

101
00:06:19,500 --> 00:06:21,439
Though she's the Leader
of the Sacred Hand Sect,

102
00:06:21,720 --> 00:06:23,120
she has never done anything evil.

103
00:06:23,639 --> 00:06:24,399
During her reign,

104
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:26,250
she has always restrained
the Martial Alliance.

105
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,879
Must we really be so ruthless?

106
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:31,920
The Chu family and the Gate Bureau
are born enemies.

107
00:06:32,720 --> 00:06:33,800
Wuxia, listen here.

108
00:06:34,240 --> 00:06:35,319
Being kind to your enemy

109
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:37,600
is being cruel to yourself.

110
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,000
Everything I do

111
00:06:39,199 --> 00:06:41,279
is to preserve
the honor of the Luo family.

112
00:06:43,120 --> 00:06:44,500
You will understand in the future.

113
00:06:50,250 --> 00:06:53,825
(Silence, Make Way)

114
00:06:57,275 --> 00:07:01,325
(Execute)

115
00:07:17,839 --> 00:07:18,439
Who's there?

116
00:07:20,120 --> 00:07:20,959
Coroner Xu.

117
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:22,680
I'm here to see Buyu.

118
00:07:22,839 --> 00:07:24,040
Miss Luo has ordered

119
00:07:24,050 --> 00:07:25,580
that no one is allowed to approach him.

120
00:07:25,839 --> 00:07:28,439
This is just some clothes and food.

121
00:07:28,800 --> 00:07:30,000
Besides, you all know

122
00:07:30,160 --> 00:07:31,759
Miss Luo and my brother-in-law

123
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:33,120
are just having a little spat.

124
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:34,920
They'll make up eventually.

125
00:07:35,439 --> 00:07:37,319
This doesn't seem right.

126
00:07:39,519 --> 00:07:40,079
Gentlemen,

127
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:42,800
please, just this once.

128
00:07:49,399 --> 00:07:50,279
Make it quick.

129
00:07:50,639 --> 00:07:51,199
Go on.

130
00:07:58,079 --> 00:07:59,959
Buyu.

131
00:08:02,000 --> 00:08:02,680
Anran?

132
00:08:04,279 --> 00:08:06,439
I've brought you some clothes

133
00:08:06,639 --> 00:08:07,519
and something to eat.

134
00:08:26,959 --> 00:08:27,879
Coroner Xu,

135
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:28,839
are you done yet?

136
00:08:36,320 --> 00:08:36,919
Dude?

137
00:08:41,300 --> 00:08:42,320
What are you trying to do?

138
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:44,399
I...

139
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:04,759
Sir.

140
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:08,612
(Execute)

141
00:09:08,679 --> 00:09:09,600
The time has come.

142
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,039
Behead her.

143
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:14,537
(Execute)

144
00:09:24,039 --> 00:09:24,639
Look!

145
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,639
Her parents must be heartbroken.

146
00:09:38,120 --> 00:09:39,080
What a young lady.

147
00:09:52,519 --> 00:09:53,190
What's happening?

148
00:09:53,720 --> 00:09:55,000
Xichuan outlaws, listen up!

149
00:09:55,279 --> 00:09:55,879
Save her!

150
00:10:00,160 --> 00:10:02,080
I knew you'd come
to raid the execution grounds.

151
00:10:03,399 --> 00:10:04,080
Kill them!

152
00:10:09,519 --> 00:10:10,120
Chang,

153
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,120
I'm here to save you.

154
00:10:24,399 --> 00:10:25,720
Commissioner Luo, quick...

155
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:26,919
Quick, think of something.

156
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,159
Don't panic, sir.

157
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:30,600
Everything is under my control.

158
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,080
Shuang!

159
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:02,759
Wuxia.

160
00:12:06,679 --> 00:12:08,360
Go. Leave now.

161
00:12:09,039 --> 00:12:10,559
Master is still waiting for you.

162
00:12:12,320 --> 00:12:13,080
Why?

163
00:12:15,399 --> 00:12:18,039
I know you've never done anything wrong.

164
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,919
Your life shouldn't be lost

165
00:12:22,510 --> 00:12:23,932
to the Luo family's selfish desires.

166
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:26,600
Go!

167
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:31,960
Wuxia...

168
00:12:32,159 --> 00:12:33,840
Chang, go! Leave now.

169
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,360
Go.

170
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:37,679
Wuxia!

171
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:46,559
Wuxia, why are you so foolish? Wuxia...

172
00:12:50,679 --> 00:12:51,360
Don't kill me.

173
00:12:54,639 --> 00:12:55,480
What do you want?

174
00:12:59,600 --> 00:13:00,159
Go!

175
00:13:01,200 --> 00:13:01,799
Stop!

176
00:13:02,159 --> 00:13:03,080
Don't anybody move!

177
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:04,960
If anything happens to me,

178
00:13:04,960 --> 00:13:06,559
you will all pay with your lives.

179
00:13:07,679 --> 00:13:08,519
Let us go,

180
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,480
or I'll kill this corrupt official.

181
00:13:10,480 --> 00:13:11,500
You're asking for death.

182
00:13:12,159 --> 00:13:12,840
Die,

183
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,480
take the Xichuan brothers

184
00:13:14,679 --> 00:13:15,279
and go!

185
00:13:15,600 --> 00:13:16,799
By the Sect Leader's command,

186
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:17,799
withdraw!

187
00:13:27,639 --> 00:13:28,799
Go now.

188
00:13:36,480 --> 00:13:37,039
Go!

189
00:13:37,639 --> 00:13:38,519
- Go now!
- Quickly!

190
00:13:38,960 --> 00:13:39,519
Go!

191
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,080
Pursue them!

192
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:42,840
- Yes!
- Yes!

193
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:47,960
Call for a physician!

194
00:13:48,720 --> 00:13:49,320
Grandfather!

195
00:13:52,519 --> 00:13:53,080
Xia...

196
00:13:55,200 --> 00:13:55,840
Grandfather,

197
00:13:57,159 --> 00:13:57,840
Wushuang,

198
00:13:59,440 --> 00:14:02,080
I didn't do this for Yunchang.

199
00:14:03,960 --> 00:14:06,519
I'm earning merit for the Luo family.

200
00:14:08,960 --> 00:14:09,960
Turn back.

201
00:14:12,960 --> 00:14:16,039
Don't keep repeating your mistakes.

202
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:17,799
Shuang,

203
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,399
take good care of Wuxia.

204
00:14:21,799 --> 00:14:22,480
Grandfather!

205
00:14:27,720 --> 00:14:28,960
The Luo family's honor

206
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,519
isn't sustained by the blood

207
00:14:34,600 --> 00:14:35,679
of the innocent.

208
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:40,840
If you don't stop now,

209
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:46,759
it will only lead

210
00:14:48,600 --> 00:14:51,080
to ruin.

211
00:15:00,799 --> 00:15:01,440
Wuxia.

212
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,799
- Wuxia!
- Wuxia!

213
00:15:04,399 --> 00:15:05,360
Wuxia...

214
00:15:07,480 --> 00:15:08,799
Wuxia!

215
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:14,799
- Wuxia!
- Wuxia!

216
00:15:17,559 --> 00:15:18,639
Wuxia!

217
00:15:22,987 --> 00:15:26,262
♪Grudges and regrets
are like strong wine♪

218
00:15:26,300 --> 00:15:29,175
♪Drink it down and let it go♪

219
00:15:29,675 --> 00:15:35,393
♪An empty cup for our love and hate♪

220
00:15:36,575 --> 00:15:39,895
♪Tears blur a fate I can't control♪

221
00:15:40,025 --> 00:15:42,945
♪Let's drink until dawn♪

222
00:15:44,113 --> 00:15:49,353
♪Behind this mask, I'll never lie♪

223
00:15:50,575 --> 00:15:52,968
♪Every reunion feels like the first♪

224
00:15:52,968 --> 00:15:56,618
♪This hidden smile will never fade♪

225
00:15:56,687 --> 00:16:00,177
♪One heart, standing by your side♪

226
00:16:00,275 --> 00:16:03,250
♪To the ends of time♪

227
00:16:03,250 --> 00:16:06,625
♪The moon traces your face♪

228
00:16:06,812 --> 00:16:10,400
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

229
00:16:10,400 --> 00:16:16,640
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

230
00:16:16,975 --> 00:16:20,190
♪A silent prayer in my soul♪

231
00:16:20,475 --> 00:16:24,013
♪Carrying my vow beneath the moon♪

232
00:16:24,300 --> 00:16:27,325
♪Hoping we never drift apart again♪

233
00:16:27,325 --> 00:16:30,425
♪On our way to forever♪

234
00:16:30,425 --> 00:16:34,275
♪The moon traces your face♪

235
00:16:34,275 --> 00:16:37,635
♪Draped in clouds, you fill my heart♪

236
00:16:37,825 --> 00:16:43,785
♪To find you
and keep our promise forever♪

237
00:16:44,862 --> 00:16:54,502
♪Just to be with you♪
